data.name: OleDbSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT ThongTinDatVe.MaTTDV, ThongTinDatVe.MaVe, ThongTinDatVe.MaCB, ThongTinDatVe.MaKH, ThongTinDatVe.SoLuongNguoi, ThongTinDatVe.NgayDat, ChuyenBay.DiemKhoiHanh, ChuyenBay.DiemDen, ChuyenBay.ThoiGianBay, ChuyenBay.NgayDi, ChuyenBay.NgayVe, KhachHang.CMND, KhachHang.tenKH, KhachHang.SDT, Ve.TinhTrangVe, Ve.GiaVe, Ve.HangBay FROM ThongTinDatVe INNER JOIN ChuyenBay ON ThongTinDatVe.MaCB = ChuyenBay.MaCB INNER JOIN KhachHang ON ThongTinDatVe.MaKH = KhachHang.MaKH INNER JOIN Ve ON ThongTinDatVe.MaVe = Ve.MaVe
